<li>Grip the bar with an overhand grip (palms facing forward), hands slightly wider than shoulder-width.</li>



<li>Inhale and engage your core as you lift the bar.</li>



<li>Exhale and press the bar overhead by extending your elbows until your arms are fully extended.&nbsp;</li>



<li>Hold for one count and focus on squeezing the shoulders.</li>



<li>Inhale as you lower the bar slowly back to the starting position.</li>
</ol>



<h4 class="wp-block-heading">TipsÂ </h4>



