<h3 class="wp-block-heading" id="Smith-Machine-Squat">Smith Machine Squat</h3>



<p><a href="https://www.endomondo.com/exercise/smith-machine-squat" target="_blank" rel="noreferrer noopener">Smith machine squats</a> are an excellent lower body strength builder for the quadriceps, glutes, and hamstrings. They follow the same movement as the traditional squat but the Smith machineâ€™s fixed path provides control and support.</p>



<p>Like the squat, this <a href="https://www.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov/pmc/articles/PMC10987311/" target="_blank" rel="noreferrer noopener nofollow">has many benefits</a> including developing the glutes and thighs, hip stabilization, and improving functional lower-body strength. The support from the machine also helps reduce lower back strain which can cause injury and discomfort.</p>



