<h3 class="wp-block-heading" id="Smith-Machine-Reverse-Lunge">Smith Machine Reverse Lunge</h3>



<p>Smith machine reverse lunges are an effective workout targeting a wide range of lower-body muscles. They strengthen the quadriceps, glutes, calves, and hamstrings. The Smith machine provides additional support for increasing the load to achieve greater muscle growth.</p>



<p>The Smith machine reverse lunge has many benefits including developing the glutes and thighs, <a href="https://www.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov/pmc/articles/PMC6006536/" target="_blank" rel="noreferrer noopener nofollow">improving balance</a>, coordination, and functional lower-body strength. The support from the machine also helps reduce lower back strain which can cause injury and discomfort.</p>



