<h2 class="wp-block-heading">Best Smith Machine Workout Routine</h2>



<p>The following program is a recommended upper-body strength routine utilizing Smith machine exercises. You can incorporate these into your next arm workout or functional strength routine in the order of your preference.</p>



<div class="wp-block-group medicine-table is-layout-constrained wp-block-group-is-layout-constrained"><div class="wp-block-group__inner-container">
